	(text "Notes while Routing:\n* C3 should be as close to VBAT as possible.\n* C4 is for bulk decoupling. Place it close to the output of the v-regulator.\n* C5-8 are for the 4 VDDs, and needs to be as close to them as possible."
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 158.75 66.04 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(face "Ubuntu Mono")
