		(uuid "28b95ca6-c9a8-4a6c-ab46-3cc2a1bff6f1")
	)
	(text "Notes while Routing:\n* Keep the ESD chip as close to the USB-C as possible\n* Keep the D+ and D- traces running perfectly parallel.\n* There should be unbroken, solid ground plane beneath the \n  entire path of the D+ and D- traces."
